description: The rallies were largely peaceful, but there was outrage when protesters tried to storm the Reichstag.
title: Germany coronavirus: Hundreds arrested in German 'anti-corona' protests

maintext: Mrs Merkel said: "We will have to live with this virus for a long time to come. It is still serious." She said it would become more challenging in the winter.
